sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User
  participant UI as X Monitor UI
  participant PX as Next.js API proxy (/api/v1)
  participant API as VPC API Lambda (/v1)
  participant DB as RDS PostgreSQL
  participant Q as SQS queue
  participant W as Compose worker Lambda
  participant CM as Compose model API

  U->>UI: Open X Monitor
  UI->>PX: GET /feed or POST /query/semantic
  PX->>API: Forward request
  API->>DB: Read feed/semantic candidates
  API-->>PX: Results
  PX-->>UI: Posts + filters + summaries

  U->>UI: Generate answer (Answer Mode)
  UI->>PX: POST /query/compose/jobs
  PX->>API: Create async compose job
  API->>DB: Insert compose_jobs(status=queued)
  API->>Q: Enqueue job_id
  API-->>UI: 202 + job_id

  loop Polling
    UI->>PX: GET /query/compose/jobs/{jobId}
    PX->>API: Read job status
    API->>DB: Fetch job row
    API-->>UI: queued/running/completed/failed
  end

  Q->>W: Deliver job
  W->>DB: Load job + retrieval context
  W->>CM: Generate grounded answer/draft
  CM-->>W: Structured response
  W->>DB: Update compose_jobs(result/status)
